data.description: Great value on our popular 3 bed/2.5 bath Abbington Plan with full daylight basement! Builder features include Granite & SS Appliances in kitchen, Luxury Vinyl Tile flooring throughout 1st floor, huge master suite w/ oversized shower and walk-in closet, large secondary bedrooms, and oversized garage. 2nd floor loft can be used as office or movie room. Great location with easy access to shopping & amenities. Home is scheduled to be complete early December. Great yard that backs to the greenway!
